      <section id="id4536846">
        <title>[LO 4.3, 2,2]</title>
        <para id="id1168510654076">Have you ever heard of a Dodo?</para>
        <para id="id1168509050564">You may have heard of this bird (the Dodo) but you will never see a live one. Man has caused its extinction!</para>
        <para id="id1168513263993">You see we must look after our earth to ensure the continuation of our precious animal kingdom.</para>
        <para id="id8265395">In a <emphasis effect="bold">play dialogue </emphasis>of ± 100 words describe to your friend another extinct animal or bird.(You will have to do some research.)</para>
        <para id="id2656073">Remember to do a rough draft and to show proof of editing before writing your final draft.</para>
        <para id="id1168510766323">Once done plot your <emphasis effect="bold">X</emphasis>! </para>
        <para id="id2901525">Check the functional writing rubric before you start!</para>
        <para id="id1168515703327"/>
