        <para id="id3045777">(<emphasis effect="bold">15</emphasis>)</para>
        <para id="id1168510865807">Now you and a partner can produce this dialogue as a role-play to the class – have fun! (You can also perhaps demonstrate the actions of the animal or make the sound it made.)</para>
